   <TextEncoding>134217984</TextEncoding>
   <SourceLine>Function SecondaryTendexCalc(Reb as double, ast as double, stl as double, blk as double, tos as double, mins as integer) As double</SourceLine>
   <SourceLine>if mins&lt;&gt;0 then</SourceLine>
   <SourceLine>return (1.25*reb + 1.33*ast + 1.5 * stl + 1.25 * blk - 1.5*tos)/mins</SourceLine>
   <SourceLine>else</SourceLine>
   <SourceLine>return 0</SourceLine>
   <SourceLine>end</SourceLine>
   <SourceLine>End Function</SourceLine>
